content.html: "Can't Help Myself" by Sun Yuan & Peng Yu. This robotic arm was programmed to keep pulling its hydraulic fluid it needs to survive back to itself, which is constantly increasingly leaking out. While programmed to do other things, eventually all it could do was fight to survive.
content.value:
"Can't Help Myself" by Sun Yuan & Peng Yu.
This robotic arm was programmed to keep pulling its hydraulic fluid it needs to survive back to itself, which is constantly increasingly leaking out. While programmed to do other things, eventually all it could do was fight to survive.
